    "visualLanguage": ["light mode", "off-white background", "blue accent", "bold editorial heading with tight tracking", "masonry grid", "image-forward"],
    "industry":       "Creative",
    "notes":          "Uses a proprietary condensed sans-serif for large headings (with extreme negative letter-spacing, e.g. -4px at 80px) and a regular-width variant for body text. The primary brand color is a vivid blue (#0057ff). All buttons use a pill shape (border-radius: 100px). The page background is off-white (#f9f9f9). The design is light, clean, and editorial — letting creative work shine. Masonry project grid has no border-radius on image thumbnails. The --be- CSS custom property namespace is comprehensive, covering spacing, color, button variants, and component tokens."
  },

